---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="页面未找到"
  description="这个页面不存在，或者已经被移动。"
  noindex
>
  <section class="not-found site-shell">
    <p class="eyebrow">404 / Lost in orbit</p>
    <h1>这里没有找到内容</h1>
    <p>链接可能已经改变，也可能只是走进了一条还没有内容的轨道。</p>
    <div class="button-row">
      <a class="button primary" href="/">返回首页</a>
      <a class="button" href="/blog/">查看文章</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .not-found {
    display: grid;
    align-content: center;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 174px);
    padding: 72px 0;
  }

  .not-found h1 {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .not-found > p:not(.eyebrow) {
    max-width: 620px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .primary {
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 55%, var(--color-line));
    background: var(--color-accent-soft);
    color: var(--color-accent-strong);
  }
</style>
